node.title: Person missing after shark sighting at Port Beach in Fremantle
node.description: A search is underway for a person who has not been seen since a shark sighting at a beach in the port city of Fremantle.
node.content: ["Authorities have launched a search for a person, believed to be male,\u00a0who has not been since a shark was sighted at Port Beach in Fremantle.", "At least three police rescue boats and two helicopters are searching the area and an ambulance has been sent to the scene.", "A number of witnesses on the beach have reported seeing the shark in the area, with some believing it was a great white.", "More to come."]
